pylmp - 用 Python 写的文本界面的 LRC MP3 播放器  使用说明
pylmp - the commandline LRC MP3 Player written in Python  README

本软件(pylmp)是在 GPLv3 的许可下发行的，它将永远免费和开源。
如果您要修改它，请公布您修改的代码。详细请见 COPYING 文件。
任何英文部分有疑义的，请参照中文文档。
This software (pylmp) is published under GPLv3,
It will be free and opensource forever.
For more details, please read the file COPYING.
If there are any problems in English document,
please follow the Chinese version of it.

* 简介
* INTRODUCTION
- 本软件用 Python 写成，是基于命令行界面的能显示LRC歌词的轻量级MP3播放器。
- This software is written in Python, it is based on command-line interface.
  It is a light-weight MP3 Player which can show LRC lyrics.
- 它不仅能在终端中运行，更是能在tty下运行。
- It can run under not only terminals but also tty.
- 歌词文件支持 ANSI、UTF-8、GB2312 以及 GBK 编码。
- It supports following encodings for the lyric file: ANSI, UTF-8, GB2312 and GBK.

* 安装
* INSTALLATION
- 打开终端（GNOME终端或xterm等）输入以下命令解压缩:
- Run a terminal (gnome-terminal or xterm, etc.), 
  and type following command to untar and unzip:
$ tar xvfz pylmp-0.1.tar.gz
- 要使用本软件，您还需要安装以下库文件:
- To use this software, you also need to install the following libraries:
! pyao, pymad
- 如果您在使用 Ubuntu, 安装过程将会很简单。只需打开终端，然后输入一下命令即可。
- If you are using Ubuntu, it will be easy to install them.
  Just run a terminal and type following command:
$ sudo apt-get install python-pyao python-pymad
- 当然，您也可以使用新利得软件包管理器搜索并装上 python-pyao 及 python-pymad。
- Of course you can use synaptic to search and install python-pyao and python-pymad.
- (可选)如果你希望能想普通命令一样使用pylmp，那么执行:
- (OPTIONAL)If you want to use pylmp just like a normal command, execute:
$ sudo ./install

* 使用
* USAGE
- 您可以这样使用它:
- You can use it like this:
$ pylmp a.mp3 [b.mp3 [c.mp3 ...]]
- 对于 a.mp3，软件会去寻找 a.lrc，对于b.mp3，软件会去寻找 b.lrc，以此类推。
- For a.mp3, the software will find a.lrc, and b.lrc for b.mp3, etc.
- 这样会在软件中产生一个播放列表。
- It will generate a playlist in the software if you do so.
- 至于具体如何操作，请看软件中的说明。
- For more details, please read the instructions in the software.

＊ 注意
＊ CAUTION
- 您的屏幕必须足够大（至少 50 × 9 个字符），否则软件将会引发错误（断言异常）！
- Your screen should be big enough (at least 50 * 9 characters),
  or it will cause an AssertionError!

